Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:08.73,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:12.01,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 你還在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.68,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真喜歡那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:19.11,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,蘋果派烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.06,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:43.16,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:47.19,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,我最最最喜歡媽媽烤的蘋果派了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.02,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:55.95,TEXT,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾達 希爾達
